# task #134 (Reconnect): with a persisted login and a healthy daemon, Reconnect restarts
# tailscaled from state and reports the honest success token (connected:<tailnet-ip>).
# No QR / no re-auth anywhere in this path — the persisted state file is the only input.
desc tailscale-lib: Reconnect from persisted login reaches Running -> connected:<ip>
invoke tslib
tsdaemon slow:10
sdfile+ .userdata/tg5040/tailscale/tailscaled.state
tsdrv reconnect
tsdrv count
expect_exit 0
expect_trace TSDRV reconnect rc=0 tok=connected:100.64.0.9
expect_trace TSDRV daemons=1
expect_file_has .userdata/tg5040/tailscale/tailscaled.log reconnect: Running again (100.64.0.9)
